ausy dw hI (jgq ivc) hukm c`l irhw hY, ausy dw hI (jgq ivc) rwj hY[ hryk jug ivc hryk jIv dy isr auqy auhI prmwqmw krn-jog kwr mukrr krdw Aw irhw hY ]1]
